title: Souvenir programme published in aid of Stan Bowles and Alzheimer's Society (Brentford Football Club Ltd) ...
text: ( Source : Brentford Football Club Ltd) Brentford are to produce their largest-ever matchday programme for the game against Queens Park Rangers on Friday 30 October to raise funds and awareness for Stan Bowles and the Alzheimer's Society .
